title: Custom Maid 3D CM3D 1.51 + Oculus Rift - Uncensored, Translated.
description:
The VR update is out and that means a new torrent that's uncensored, translated and awesome! The VR version is 1.03.
Sadly I couldn't find a working SPIV. (Skills pack 4)

The game is in English ONLY!


VR tip : Press the left shift to see all the different settings. Use WASD to move around and Q/E to turn around, there's sadly no DK2 positional tracking in version 1.03.
